creator: K.J.P Games
descriptionHtml:
Classic-a game in which you will not let the falling cards fall into the Inferno!
-Feel the rhythm of the flight of these cards or ask your own!
- Upgrade your gaming skills!
- Collect rewards!
- Change the background of the game to your taste and color!
-Participate in competitive mode and hold out as long as possible, while beating all the players standing in the ranking
and get cool prizes!
And just anneal it just like in Tik Tok or Instagram!
EDM Music.
descriptionShort: Don't let the falling cards fall into the very hell!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Changed the card drop balance,
Changed the mechanics of increasing difficulty,
Fixed a bug related to the leaderboard
Added two new tracks to the General music collection these are:
Tokyo Machine - Spooky and Yusuf Alev - Yoros
We are waiting for your suggestions in our discord:https://discord.gg/2Qxkkr6

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
-Major workshop update now you can add your own content or upload content created by other players without leaving the game.
- Rebalance of falling cards(now the game will become more difficult, but more fun)
-New AWP model(now in 3D and Yes it will now follow your aim)
--The shot of cards and complete their dismemberment and destruction
- Simplify training
- Optimize and reduce the weight of the game from 78 MB to 33 MB now the game will go even on the calculator.
